{"tid":469075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消委會】一日三餐茶記「例牌」=狂食脂肪+鈉 超世衞建議1、2倍","createTime":"2017-11-15T03:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T06:28:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e884fb212b03b842aec0f00dbb0b4a09ddf21d95","tid":469075,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510715229_9c2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510715229_9c2c.jpg&h=0b0868b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消費者委員會與食物安全中心合作，測試市面10款小菜合共100個樣本，發現多款港人經常點選的小菜都屬高鹽或高脂，如果一日三餐都在茶餐廳用膳，看似平常的餐單，其實多款營養素都已超標，其鈉攝取量隨時遠高於世界衞生組織建議上限。本港不少打工仔、都市人都屬單身一族或「無飯」家庭，會以快餐店、茶餐廳作為一日三餐的「飯堂」。消委會模擬港人在茶餐廳一日三餐的「例牌」餐單：早餐是餐肉蛋即食麵、熱奶茶；午餐是乾炒牛河、凍檸茶；晚餐是西蘭花炒魚塊、中式湯、白飯。<br />\n<br />\n如以上述的餐單為例，一人食用的話，幾乎全部營養素攝入量都會超出世衛建議的每日攝取限量，其中鈉的攝入量達5,500毫克，是世衞建議的275%，總脂肪達99克，是建議的149%，飽和脂肪則有23克，超出建議5%，能量則達2,400千卡，較建議攝入量高19%，糖含量為49克，是全日建議攝入限量的 97%。<br />\n<br />\n消委會指，如果再有吃其他零食或飲品，糖的攝入量亦隨時超標。消委會提醒消費者，港人常見的高血壓、心血管疾病和冠心病，都與日常飲食習慣有密切關係，建議消費者外出用膳，應以少鹽、少糖、少油為原則，以減低患相關疾病的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460016&d=dVuD9CyTRKGt4QCszSyEApUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=f51b7405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460016&h=f09454d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460016</a>"},{"pid":"55e56f5e19a4c2c75b1814cf26b5949f311ca59d","tid":469075,"uid":44333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"咁你有咩好建議呀"},{"pid":"e9c1f1f5a14330e2cb6cfaab9d5332aa8c3deba1","tid":469075,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"啲杯麵個個鈉含量都過2000mg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e623841e3bca1df55988696d00edba5e5ffbf6","tid":469075,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"張圖d野食幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab528f4df115ea0189000e5b6782ddc6698fd2c","tid":469075,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"消委會呢d 雖然講唔出咩大道理 但係就好撚親切嘅測驗真係好撚正"},{"pid":"1e59815b7e10313680676ff55837830a6ecaf8dd","tid":469075,"uid":18167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"3餐都茶記只係超呢個數我覺得好滿意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455358963187b90ae439e5cda24b543412685d68","tid":469075,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張圖d野食幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望完好撚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a74b3881de22a652d66cad35096510acde5edc7","tid":469075,"uid":23416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"食撚屎算啦"},{"pid":"37adc67a26c34f97f5d9af9ae8a16742adb70bd6","tid":469075,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b2174ab90d9e6120c69a41356f610fe6eaad918","tid":469075,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張圖d野食幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望完好撚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日有得咁食都唔錯了<br />\n<br />\n餐肉煎蛋麵跟熱奶茶, 太興35 定37啦 $37<br />\n<br />\n干炒牛河, 中午食四十蚊走唔甩, 凍飲加三蚊即$43<br />\n<br />\n夜晚食到西蘭花炒魚柳. 仲加碗例湯,  60蚊算平啦<br />\n<br />\n一百就咁計都百三蚊啦"},{"pid":"c6100854aed6ba9a52c1706d48302a5e09307a5e","tid":469075,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食西蘭花炒魚塊都超標咁仲有咩可以食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蒸肉餅?</blockquote><br />\n飲水練仙"},{"pid":"9293e59c0d0eb75553d7aa22d5c0f76c460a29fc","tid":469075,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食西蘭花炒魚塊都超標咁仲有咩可以食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蒸肉餅?</blockquote><br />\n富臨鹹蛋肉餅最多鈉 粟米魚塊+蝦仁炒蛋健康啲係假象？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510712589_e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510712589_e4e1.jpg&h=979b4f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消費者委員會與食物安全中心合作，測試市面10款小菜合共100個樣本，發現多款港人經常點選的小菜都屬高鹽或高脂，其中鹹蛋蒸肉餅的鈉含量最<br />\n高，其次是粟米魚塊及欖菜肉鬆四季豆，而鹹蛋蒸肉餅的總脂肪含量亦屬最高。其中富臨酒家的鹹蛋蒸肉餅是樣本中鈉含量最高，每100克含量有730毫克鈉，屬高鈉食物；美心MX及新釗記的粟火魚塊，每100克含量有570毫克鈉；東城酒家的欖菜肉鬆四季豆，每100克含量有560毫克鈉。<br />\n<br />\n是次測試涵蓋100個小菜樣本，分別來自中式酒樓、茶餐廳及快餐店。結果顯示，10款小菜當中，鹹蛋蒸肉餅的平均鈉含量最高，平均每100克含530毫克，100個樣本中鈉含量最高的首3位，均是鹹蛋蒸肉餅，最高的每100克含730毫克鈉，第2、3位同樣含650毫克鈉。根據食安中心的指引，每 100 克含超過600毫克鈉的食物，可界定為「高鈉」食物，3個鈉含量最高的鹹蛋蒸肉餅樣本均超出此水平，成為「高鈉」食物。<br />\n<br />\n是次測試鈉含量僅次於鹹蛋蒸肉餅的粟米魚塊和欖菜肉鬆四季豆，平均每100克含450毫克，蝦仁炒蛋緊隨其後，平均每100克含440毫克鈉。至於味道酸甜的菠蘿咕嚕肉，平均每100克含240毫克鈉，在10款小菜當中鈉含量最低。不過，雖然這類味道酸甜的小菜，鈉含量或會較低，但糖含量亦會相對較高，菠蘿咕嚕肉平均每100克含10克糖，以最高糖含量樣本計算吃1人份餐已佔近每天最高建議攝入量；中式牛柳亦類似，鈉含量平均只是每100克含340 毫克鈉，在10款小菜當中排第7，但糖含量每100克就有6.9克，僅次於菠蘿咕嚕肉。<br />\n<br />\n脂肪含量方面，首3位是鹹蛋蒸肉餅、蝦仁炒蛋及菠蘿咕嚕肉，每100克的總脂肪含量分別為20克、18克及15克。按食安中心的指引，每100克的總脂肪含量高於20克，便可界定為「高脂肪」食物。是次測試有7個樣本達此水平，包括4個鹹蛋蒸肉餅、2個蝦仁炒蛋及1個中式牛柳的樣本。<br />\n<br />\n消費會今次測試亦發現同一款小菜由不同食肆烹調，其營養素含量相差可達數倍，反映食肆只要花點心思，便可為食客烹調低鹽的健康菜式。食肆亦可以天然食材代替調味料，令菜式更為健康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460001&d=dVuD9CyTRKGt4QCszSyEApUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6b40ac0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460001&h=502345d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460001</a>"},{"pid":"c9e1c16367513d9919389062d9716dc4095ff7d3","tid":469075,"uid":54223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"光合作用最健康啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2257741fa645b7e646c0c63e972d94108430f52","tid":469075,"uid":121546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"日日食依垃圾食物都咁長命,轉食健康食物既話要等到幾時先可以安息"},{"pid":"42b86e778b5ecc78547a17bf1e22bc7a95519c15","tid":469075,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"所以我日日淨吊鹽水,係就係肚餓不過死唔去可以返工"},{"pid":"639a260d6d4dea7f5f1e25193cd821d321edc464","tid":469075,"uid":2521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"居然1日3食3餐先超2倍<br />\n茶記都算有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01da1de4d281625df9a4b1dff49